data.description: New and Improved! This brick Ranch style home has been beautifully updated and sits on almost an acre lot! This home features many improvements: Lime washed brick with wood panel trim, fully fenced yard in front/back and newly updated fencing along RV Parking entrance with an automatic opening RV Gate, mature lawn, 9X26 shop/shed with 240 power, gas fireplace in front den, heated floors in hall and master baths, Nest thermostat, UV filter for the well installed 2 years ago, Furnace replaced 1 year ago and Septic pumped within the last 2 months, vinyl plank flooring throughout main living area and hall baths, large kitchen island with Butcher Block countertop and space for mini fridge, new range vent/stove hood, subway tile backsplash in kitchen, built-in entryway nook/storage area, 8 foot panoramic fireplace with slate tile and floating shelves installed, extended concrete patio with 16x16 pergola and pasture has been wired for sprinklers. Dusk to Dawn lighting installed along the driveway.
